Ugochukwu Henrietta Oha (amụrụ na Julai 18, 1992 na Houston, Texas) bụ onye Naijiria nke Amerika na-agba egwuregwu basketbọọlụ
Ọ zọrọ mpi na Olympik nke 2004 ya na otu egwuregwu basketbọọlụ ụmụnwaanyị nke Naijiria ma gụụ akwụkwọ na Mahadum George Washington. Oha gara ụlọ akwụkwọ nke Alief Hastings High na Houston.
